OL,3,CResident doctors vote to continue
OL,4,Cstriking over next six months
OL,6,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,7,Fresident doctors committee has voted
OL,8,Fto extend their right to industrial
OL,9,Faction for a further six months.
OL,11,FThe vote extends the BMA's mandate for
OL,12,Fstrike action, after their previous
OL,13,Fmandate expired in January.
OL,15,FSome 53% of eligible members took part
OL,16,Fin a ballot to continue industrial
OL,17,Faction, with 93% voting yes, the BMA
OL,18,Fsaid.
