OL,6,F"A deal is there to be done: a new
OL,7,Fjobs package and an offer raising pay
OL,8,Ffairly over several years can be
OL,9,Fworked out through good will on both
OL,10,Fsides, in the interests of patients,
OL,11,Fstaff and the whole NHS.
OL,13,F"And now that the mandate for strike
OL,14,Faction is confirmed for six months,
OL,15,Fthe Government has nowhere to run and
OL,16,Fno means of running out the clock.
