OL,3,CResident doctors vote to continue
OL,4,Cstriking over next six months
OL,6,FA Department for Health and Social
OL,7,FCare spokesperson said: "On top of a
OL,8,F28.9% pay rise over the last three
OL,9,Fyears, this government is continuing
OL,10,Fto work with the BMA to address the
OL,11,Fissues resident doctors face in their
OL,12,Fcareers, including fast-tracking
OL,13,Flegislation to prioritise home grown
OL,14,Fmedical graduates for specialty
OL,15,Ftraining places.
