OL,3,CResident doctors vote to continue
OL,4,Cstriking over next six months
OL,6,F"The government has been in intensive
OL,7,Fand constructive discussions with the
OL,8,FBMA resident doctors committee since
OL,9,Fthe start of the new year to try and
OL,10,Fbring an end to the damaging cycle of
OL,11,Fstrikes and avoid further unnecessary
OL,12,Fdisruption for patients and NHS staff.
OL,14,F"We hope that these talks result in an
OL,15,Fagreement that works for everyone, so
OL,16,Fthat there is not any more strike
OL,17,Faction by resident doctors in 2026."
OL,19,FResident doctors last staged a full
OL,20,Fwalkout from 17 to 22 December. There
OL,21,Fwere also strikes in July and November.
